/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呢個決定係因為我依家蛋白尿情況<br />\n時好時壞<br />\n有時候屙尿無泡<br />\n有時就都幾多下<br />\n所以我諗住觀察耐d 再做進一步打算"},{"pid":"8b440c801381577ddcdffed87e69110f08bc0c27","tid":407073,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n重等10月尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呢個決定係因為我依家蛋白尿情況<br />\n時好時壞<br />\n有時候屙尿無泡<br />\n有時就都幾多下<br />\n所以我諗住觀察耐d 再做進一步打算</blockquote><br />\n體重有無跌？"},{"pid":"e72eedae2080046ee3c00233ba195eacfa22da1d","tid":407073,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n重等10月尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呢個決定係因為我依家蛋白尿情況<br />\n時好時壞<br />\n有時候屙尿無泡<br />\n有時就都幾多下<br />\n所以我諗住觀察耐d 再做進一步打算</blockquote><br />\n睇醫生啦屌<br />\n觀察耐啲 個腎就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53aa719b644f2a8275197614d0f6a8759559068a","tid":407073,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"唔驗點知蛋白尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926593c9d7d03183822629857c7271e4a0e196f0","tid":407073,"uid":25490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"要投定胎了"},{"pid":"df68230a3428b55809a0a3ccdf07641d17881e67","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n體重有無跌？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無"},{"pid":"660f2aec89a8b75c3b40e5c4f92be86e3d915f2f","tid":407073,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike"