ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fbc37946e064467a41491700d3c70043aa0b58","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多數無事<br />\n<br />\n可能漏精<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\n去睇醫生啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n漏精我之前試過 但今次唔同<br />\n所以理論上唔會係漏精<br />\n加上我生活習慣唔好 所以我諗今次尿起泡兼長時間唔散<br />\n應該同我個腎功能受損有關<br />\n<br />\n不過都唔排除會有漏精呢個可能性既"},{"pid":"7eaef81c95010d76ac448a580a78234ede89b6d2","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>糖尿？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無三高"},{"pid":"efbc72172e31040ca69c0bf7213d1b9dd2f9ec91","tid":407073,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真蛋白尿有泡之餘d泡沖唔走<br />\n驚ge咪去藥房咪張試紙驗尿</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1分鐘都未散<br />\n今個星期六搵下邊到有尿蛋白試紙</blockquote><br />\n笑9死<br />\n驗都未驗就話自己蛋白尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2d6842b29ef94b9d50ecbe46004c667c4c2b63","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日朝早起身都好多泡<br />\n<br />\n驗尿抽血無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁希望我都會好似巴打咁 無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bce4757f7fcd22d1d6ae0653ccc1304e4bcc9f9","tid":407073,"uid":48065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日日朝早起身都好多泡<br />\n<br />\n驗尿抽血無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁希望我都會好似巴打咁 無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果同你講 普通驗尿其實未必驗得出 <br />\n你會唔會更淆"},{"pid":"c547c90ba6a7fa2b91d4c5d84aed8394fe7495e8","tid":407073,"uid":144366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"食返多啲蛋黃"},{"pid":"28df6a33881a4941