\n<br />\n平時飲水都多既 3000毫升一日 但係d泡都係會堆積係到<br />\n1分鐘都可以唔散 更加試過屙尿去馬桶側邊流落去<br />\n等佢無咁衝擊 但係都會有少量既泡積聚係側邊"},{"pid":"62a132636b5807edd5019d5b13d99d8bea7b9240","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腎可能有事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nyep"},{"pid":"7ea95e00ab286934415eb3b578a0087de5f1d54b","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前都有泡，去睇完醫生驗完都話正常。<br />\n其實有泡唔一定係蛋白尿。<br />\n樓主唔洗咁擔心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係杞人憂天啦<br />\n不過話哂關乎到個腎 認真d面對都好既"},{"pid":"009550aaa1d1647034c8aa345d3255316b9d181b","tid":407073,"uid":99745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:09:13.000Z","msg":"仲等咩 去驗一驗都係百零蚊炸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c042a4c4df197d2e8e109ae3efff8c15d59564","tid":407073,"uid":82612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"其實咁高屙尿又朝早第一泡有泡正常架<br />\n最緊要睇啲泡會唔會散<br />\n唔散就好睇醫生啦！"},{"pid":"4a5c19f5a30fcd116c77c72518a76afee1c2a5a4","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲等咩 去驗一驗都係百零蚊炸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無咩介紹"},{"pid":"17467f0a25be83f2ee096c9fbc1ef9599d20848c","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:10:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實咁高屙尿又朝早第一泡有泡正常架<br />\n最緊要睇啲泡會唔會散<br />\n唔散就好睇醫生啦！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n觀察左1分鐘都未散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a93f0c30f6fddeef069891c4a0c26b2d0570ee","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"18fd57c6a2f514ac9d44c83381a141d912e817f3","tid":407073,"uid":7050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime