0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n重等10月尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呢個決定係因為我依家蛋白尿情況<br />\n時好時壞<br />\n有時候屙尿無泡<br />\n有時就都幾多下<br />\n所以我諗住觀察耐d 再做進一步打算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係多泡定蛋白尿<br />\n你睇清楚未"},{"pid":"c10860eb6dabc07ee3ca4dc952a2b601d6460b9d","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>j少啲大橋未久</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無J好耐"},{"pid":"7aae12d67f63ab7a589bf490a25a49d1f0cc97fd","tid":407073,"uid":99745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好快d睇啊巴打<br />\n我以為無乜事睇完醫生結果係凝血症<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塞住左個腎嘅血管搞到個功能唔work(好似係<br />\n你都係快d睇下醫生一陣唔知關其他乜野事<br />\n遲左就好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打呢個病食咩藥"},{"pid":"7311707bbef83fc86589e302841840d73a3d1dc7","tid":407073,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都有呢個問題<br />\n巴打幾歲?<br />\n<br />\n係咪可以做定身後事?"},{"pid":"9bf6e16bbc72422f94bd7cbc5658bf017ae19e83","tid":407073,"uid":48065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:33:29.000Z","msg":"咁樣討一討論 聽日都去驗一驗先 <br />\n近排起身啲泡真心多同唔散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd561ba21fd3c334d4c3d5acff26ae9ba4e6d12","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係多泡定蛋白尿<br />\n你睇清楚未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n澄明返先<br />\n<br />\n點解我會覺得自己個d係病性蛋白尿而非泡又或者假性蛋白<br />\n<br />\n我由9月8號開始觀察緊自己身體狀況<br />\n平均日飲3000毫升兼盡量保持飲食清淡<br />\n每日晨早既尿 正如咁多位巴打所講 有泡係正常<br />\n但係泡沫停留既時間都幾撚長下<br />\n起碼超過一分鐘 我都廢撚到慢慢睇佢幾耐先會散直接沖走<br />\n而平時屙尿既泡沫都會因我既飲食而有所改變<br />\n例如我某一日燒烤 打邊爐 瘋狂食肉<br />\n起泡既情況都會激增而且一分鐘都唔會散<br />\n<br />\n就咁平時飲食 我依家都盡量進行低蛋白飲食<br />\n去調節一下自己身體<br />\n泡沫數量情況係有改善 有時屙尿重會無泡<br />\n所以我得出一個比較冒昧既結論<br />\n就係我既腎臟功能受損令到我有蛋白尿既情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：有2個月 服用藥物既紀錄"},{"pid":"6d63cea49bd2240b0cac9f4e5c6c2a1e83a2a87d","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都有呢個問題<br />\n巴打幾歲?<br />\n<br />\n係咪可以做定身後事?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後生仔 20出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身後事就唔洗<br />\n我比我戶口你 你過筆數過去就可以搞掂 無手尾跟"},{"pid":"c47007d6f8b7276fb1fef97cc0073bd8473dce11","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樣討一討論 聽日都去驗一驗先 <br />\n近排起身啲泡真心多同唔散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086c34a1c7cd52d752981fbe48d78dfcb84359b4","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b35ce3b4b41802e5a3772b59651f547c9c0fdb51","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"啊 重有 我呢排失眠左好耐 無覺唔訓<br />\n唔排除因為咁身體機能變差"},{"pid":"8d57935a9f19f7903d106a01e1349ec9a164fac2","tid":407073,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啊 重有 我呢排失眠左好耐 無覺<ins