\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2dc4c1063f92e6858ca044963e297cd9b329bd","tid":407073,"uid":138390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n睇醫生啦屌<br />\n觀察耐啲 個腎就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無醫生好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有<br />\nSt Theresa 朱國康醫生<br />\n驗血同驗mid stream urine $1k倒<br />\n醫生好好 希望幫倒巴打你"},{"pid":"4d29b924346a66704d49428940bdcd829f1adf0f","tid":407073,"uid":29962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"飲多d水喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a12f9efffa0ff9a3e91c56f1ee0ace887144ee2","tid":407073,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我最近屙尿都好多泡<br />\n用試紙驗左<br />\n冇蛋白<br />\n但ph值好高<br />\n代表咩?</blockquote><br />\n泡會散？</blockquote><br />\n會<br />\n但要等一陣囉"},{"pid":"c3c497b99d8db39ab91b9729713806ba1ecfbf04","tid":407073,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:57:23.000Z","msg":"去力威"},{"pid":"83fa159c25cb509f75ff1db7d7d942865b0ced46","tid":407073,"uid":138390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最近屙尿都好多泡<br />\n用試紙驗左<br />\n冇蛋白<br />\n但ph值好高<br />\n代表咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飲食習慣同尿ph値有直接關係<br />\n例如 食得多生果，菜，奶類就會令尿變鹼<br />\n反之 食得多蛋，芝士，肉類，蕃茄等等就會令尿變酸<br />\n<br />\n唔洗太擔心既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e1c9dee1aca779ca4357048d16794a2830d9e9","tid":407073,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T09:01:41.000Z","msg":"我起身去廁所多泡，平時會不停飲水，飲得多去得多反而冇事，然後loop"},{